    "summary": "The user asks for an explanation of the South China Sea disputes, specifically focusing on the legality of maritime claims following the 2016 Permanent Court of Arbitration ruling. The assistant provides a factual overview of the ruling's impact on the \"nine-dash line\" and discusses the tension between international law and geopolitical/military realities.",
